<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en-US">
<head>  
  <title>A MadLibs</title>
  <link rel="stylesheet" href="https://stackpath.bootstrapcdn.com/bootstrap/4.5.0/css/bootstrap.min.css" integrity="sha384-9aIt2nRpC12Uk9gS9baDl411NQApFmC26EwAOH8WgZl5MYYxFfc+NcPb1dKGj7Sk" crossorigin="anonymous">
</head>
<body>
  <div class="container">
      <div id="story">
      <h1>Comprehensive Visitation</h1>
      <p>
        One day, <span class="person1">@Model.Name</span> and <span class="person2">@Model.AnotherName</span> were walking through the woods, when suddenly a giant <span class="animal">@Model.Animal</span> appeared. "<span class="exclamation">@Model.Exclamation</span>", <span class="person1">@Model.Name</span> Shouted. The two of them <span class="verb">@Model.PastTenseVerb</span> as quickly possible, and when they were safe, <span class="person1">@Model.Name</span> and <span class="person2">@Model.AnotherName</span> gave each other a giant <span class="noun">@Model.Noun</span>.
      </p>
    </div>
  </div>
</body>
</html>